1
00:01:32,460 --> 00:01:39,880
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,190 --> 00:01:42,870
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:44,210 --> 00:01:45,800
Ke, you're here.

4
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:48,780
Brother Lu.

5
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:50,840
When we don't see each other

6
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:51,970
for days, do you feel like

7
00:01:51,970 --> 00:01:53,039
we're happier than before

8
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,380
when we meet again?

9
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:56,530
Why would we be apart for days?

10
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:58,560
Well,

11
00:01:58,920 --> 00:01:59,979
for example,

12
00:02:00,070 --> 00:02:01,420
I have my affairs to settle,

13
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:02,560
and you have yours,

14
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:03,850
and we won't bother each other.

15
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:05,650
Aren't your affairs my affairs?

16
00:02:05,870 --> 00:02:07,570
You won't bother me,
and I won't bother you.

17
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:08,970
What kind of talk is that?

18
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,479
Do you know that

19
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:13,100
I need some peace and quiet too?

20
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:16,170
I also need that sweet feeling
of missing someone.

21
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:22,829
Ke, are you tired of me

22
00:02:23,470 --> 00:02:25,000
and want to get away from me?

23
00:02:25,200 --> 00:02:27,000
I'm saying one thing,
and you're saying another.

24
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,320
We're not even talking
about the same thing.

25
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:31,120
Then what are you talking about?

26
00:02:35,060 --> 00:02:36,970
Why did you send Lu Yi to follow me?

27
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,860
He wasn't protecting you.

28
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,660
He was protecting you.

29
00:02:47,220 --> 00:02:49,470
The Marquis Wu'an has been quiet lately,

30
00:02:49,470 --> 00:02:50,800
which is very abnormal.

31
00:02:51,190 --> 00:02:52,920
There must be something fishy.

32
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:55,550
Now that you're a top marriage broker at
the Official Matchmaking Agency,

33
00:02:55,550 --> 00:02:57,079
I have to be extra cautious.

34
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,400
But

35
00:02:59,470 --> 00:03:01,400
I feared the truth might scare you,

36
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,100
so I had Lu Yi guard you secretly.

37
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:09,580
I thought you were having someone watch me

38
00:03:09,870 --> 00:03:11,600
to keep tabs on my whereabouts.

39
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:15,210
Brother Lu.

40
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:19,470
I won't blame you so easily again.

41
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,680
It's okay if you blame me.

42
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,800
But from now on,

43
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,030
please don't talk about
missing each other from afar

44
00:03:27,030 --> 00:03:29,160
or not disturbing each other anymore.

45
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:30,800
Alright, I understand.

46
00:03:31,790 --> 00:03:32,490
Promise.

47
00:03:34,390 --> 00:03:36,780
Okay, I promise.

48
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:49,290
Uncle, you asked to see me.

49
00:03:49,290 --> 00:03:50,620
What orders do you have?

50
00:03:52,079 --> 00:03:53,880
Xibao Pavilion's Lu Zhuxi

51
00:03:54,270 --> 00:03:57,200
went to that old man Zhu's house
to propose marriage.

52
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,829
