53
00:03:59,090 --> 00:04:01,210
really marries that brat,

54
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,330
where does that leave my dignity?

55
00:04:05,690 --> 00:04:07,940
Yes, Uncle, I know what I must do now.

56
00:04:34,670 --> 00:04:35,870
Give it to me.

57
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:39,190
