58
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:41,830
Were the betrothal gifts
not substantial enough?

59
00:04:41,830 --> 00:04:43,310
Besides the existing betrothal gifts,

60
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:44,920
how about I add a few more shops?

61
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,560
It's not about the betrothal gifts.

62
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,560
How could Lord Zhu possibly
value betrothal gifts

63
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,300
more than Yanyan's marriage?

64
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,810
Then what's the reason?

65
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,490
You rascal.

66
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:02,480
Your sister-in-law and I
have worked so hard

67
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,540
for your marriage.

68
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,770
And here you are,
drinking tea in the cool breeze,

69
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:10,130
not worried at all.

70
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:14,870
Brother Lu, it's not settled yet.

71
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:18,010
It will be soon.

72
00:05:18,210 --> 00:05:19,010
No escape now.

73
00:05:19,890 --> 00:05:20,480
Sit down.

74
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,620
Deputy Chief!

75
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,760
Deputy Chief.

76
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:26,510
I brought down the things

77
00:05:26,510 --> 00:05:28,170
you wanted from the mountian.

78
00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:31,580
Brother and sister-in-law,
for your great kindness,

79
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:32,970
I am deeply grateful.

80
00:05:33,240 --> 00:05:35,950
However, I need to go back and
organize some things now.

81
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,270
Regarding my marriage,

82
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,510
please don't worry,

83
00:05:38,530 --> 00:05:40,130
I have my own brilliant plan.

84
00:05:40,830 --> 00:05:41,780
Lu Yi, let's go.

85
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:42,480
Let's go.

86
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:44,110
Go, go.

87
00:05:47,690 --> 00:05:49,230
Is this okay?

88
00:05:51,190 --> 00:05:51,620
Here.

89
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:55,460
This time, it's twice as much as before.

90
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:57,990
I wonder if Lord Zhu will be satisfied?

91
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,500
Brother Lu,

92
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:02,080
you really came well-prepared this time.

93
00:06:02,080 --> 00:06:04,160
Although Lord Zhu won't care
just for the betrothal gifts,

94
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,790
we still need to show our sincerity.

95
00:06:05,790 --> 00:06:07,520
What's the point of our efforts

96
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:10,730
when Lu Zhuxi has been
holed up in his room for days

97
00:06:10,770 --> 00:06:11,970
doing god knows what?

98
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,420
Sister Pan'er.

99
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,420
Please ask young Mr. Lu to come out.

100
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,480
We should head out.

101
00:06:16,690 --> 00:06:17,220
Alright.

102
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:19,570
Brother!

103
00:06:21,330 --> 00:06:22,840
What's in this bundle?

104
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:23,460
Lu Yi.

105
00:06:30,340 --> 00:06:31,270
[Diary]

106
00:06:33,310 --> 00:06:34,600
You sent Lu Yi back to the mountain

107
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,640
to get these?

108
00:06:35,730 --> 00:06:36,550
Yes.

109
00:06:38,220 --> 00:06:39,310
What are these?

110
00:06:38,409 --> 00:06:39,180
[Diary]

111
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:43,120
In the winter of the Guiyou year,
heavy snow fell on the mountain.

112
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:46,480
My brother trained daily, after which
he would be soaked through with sweat.

113
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:49,080
Yet he stayed by me,
tending food and medicine.

114
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:51,820
Our father was obsessed with martial arts
and rarely cared for us.

115
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:54,030
Thankfully, I had my brother's protection.

116
00:06:54,030 --> 00:06:55,430
So you've kept all these.

117
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,610
I...

118
00:06:57,290 --> 00:06:58,409
Stop reading.

119
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,380
These are meant for Yanyan to read.

120
00:07:00,380 --> 00:07:03,020
What? As the matchmaker,
I can't read them?

121
00:07:03,070 --> 00:07:04,740
After Yanyan has read them,

122
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,350
I'll show you the parts about Brother.

123
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,620
My parts

124
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:10,690
are only for Yanyan to read.

125
00:07:11,210 --> 00:07:13,020
Ke, let him be.

126
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:15,480
He probably even recorded

127
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,090
how many times he cried each day,

128
00:07:17,090 --> 00:07:18,400
and how he was afraid of the dark
and wouldn't get out of bed.

129
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,120
Brother!

130
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:20,930
Never mind then,

131
00:07:20,930 --> 00:07:22,260
I won't read it.

132
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:28,550
I wrote about my life on
the mountain growing up,

133
00:07:28,580 --> 00:07:30,720
and my daily longing

134
00:07:30,740 --> 00:07:31,400
and joy

135
00:07:31,470 --> 00:07:32,730
after meeting Yanyan.

136
00:07:32,830 --> 00:07:35,360
I want to show all these to
Yanyan and Lord Zhu,

137
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,150
so they can understand me better.

138
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:37,790
This way,

139
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:40,480
Lord Zhu will feel comfortable
entrusting Yanyan to me.

140
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,830
This bundle of writings

141
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:43,890
is indeed more precious than any treasure.

142
00:07:43,890 --> 00:07:46,820
Don't worry, this marriage
will definitely happen.

143
