[Zhu's Mansion]

144
00:07:52,620 --> 00:07:56,030
[Diary]

145
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,640
Yanyan.

146
00:07:56,670 --> 00:08:00,540
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

147
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:02,010
[In late spring of the You year,
my brother and I went out to play.]

148
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:03,390
[The weather was nice. Not a cloud
in the sky. We came to a little river.]

149
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:13,540
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

150
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:12,540
These are all records of Zhuxi's past.

151
00:08:12,930 --> 00:08:13,920
Not just the past,

152
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:16,320
but also all my thoughts
since meeting you.

153
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,470
Yes,

154
00:08:17,770 --> 00:08:19,020
I just took a peek,

155
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:21,380
and this Mr. Lu wouldn't
let me read more,

156
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:24,000
saying he wanted Yanyan
to be his first reader.

157
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,810
He

158
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:27,480
has given himself to you completely
without holding back.

159
00:08:27,480 --> 00:08:29,750
It's truly sincere and touching indeed.

160
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,070
Ke.

161
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:33,669
How could you say something
so embarrassing?

162
00:08:33,610 --> 00:08:36,870
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

163
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:35,450
After you read this,

164
00:08:35,630 --> 00:08:37,270
I hope you'll understand me better,

165
00:08:37,270 --> 00:08:39,200
and know how I truly feel about you.

166
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:44,760
[Cuiwen Pavilion]

167
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,600
I'll go get Grandfather right away.

168
00:08:44,380 --> 00:08:45,010
Wait.

169
00:08:45,230 --> 00:08:46,540
Let's go together.

170
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:48,630
This time, we'll surely move Lord Zhu.

171
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:50,040
Alright, let's go.

172
