Grandfather?

180
00:09:20,500 --> 00:09:21,530
Grandfather!

181
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:22,720
Grandfather?

182
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:23,830
Grandfather?

183
00:09:24,410 --> 00:09:25,290
Grandfather!

184
00:09:25,490 --> 00:09:26,400
Grandfather!

185
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,830
Grandfather, it can't be!

186
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:30,620
Grandfather, it can't be!

187
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:34,080
Grandfather, don't leave me!

188
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,090
Grandfather!

189
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,550
Grandfather!

190
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,500
[Dowry List]

191
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:41,490
Don't leave me.

192
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:43,630
Grandfather!

193
00:09:44,230 --> 00:09:45,130
Yanyan!

194
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:46,520
Grandfather.

195
00:09:48,130 --> 00:09:48,850
Yanyan!

196
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:55,310
Someone!

197
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,280
My Lady.

198
00:10:00,270 --> 00:10:01,060
Lord Zhu!

199
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,230
Go fetch a doctor.

200
00:10:02,230 --> 00:10:03,360
Hurry, get a doctor!

201
00:10:03,630 --> 00:10:05,230
No need for a doctor anymore.

202
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:07,380
Report it to the authorities at once.

203
00:10:08,060 --> 00:10:11,750
Lord Zhu, who could have done this?

204
00:10:13,790 --> 00:10:15,410
[Dowry List]

205
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:19,170
Lord Zhu.

206
00:10:29,790 --> 00:10:30,390
Lord Zhu.

207
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:31,480
Lord Zhu.

208
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:42,080
Brother, Yanyan has
already gone back to her room.

209
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:44,110
Is there anything else I can do here?

210
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:46,210
Judging from the rigor mortis,

211
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:48,340
he's been dead for several hours.

212
