[Zhu's Mansion]

219
00:11:17,030 --> 00:11:17,950
Grandfather.

220
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:26,550
Yanyan, don't be afraid. I'm here.

221
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:27,410
Grandfather.

222
