Grandfather, don't go.

223
00:11:31,010 --> 00:11:31,800
Don't go.

224
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:34,940
Yanyan, I'm here.

225
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,700
Don't be scared.

226
00:11:37,900 --> 00:11:40,740
From now on, I'll always be with you,

227
00:11:40,770 --> 00:11:42,630
