233
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:20,550
what if Yanyan does something foolish?

234
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:21,260
And also,

235
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:23,110
who on earth killed Lord Zhu?

236
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:25,240
What if this person comes back
to harm Yanyan?

237
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,680
Ke, don't worry.

238
00:12:27,130 --> 00:12:28,750
Zhuxi will definitely protect Miss Zhu.

239
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:30,180
We're under the Emperor's nose

240
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:32,580
and a minister was murdered
in his own home.

241
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:33,910
Who could be so ruthless

242
00:12:33,910 --> 00:12:34,670
and brazen?

243
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,340
I heard that a few days ago,

244
00:12:36,350 --> 00:12:38,880
Lord Zhu embarrassed
Marquis Wu'an in court.

245
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:39,670
And before that,

246
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:40,750
he rejected

247
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:42,180
Marquis Wu'an's marriage proposal.

248
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:43,440
If anyone had a grudge,

249
00:12:44,210 --> 00:12:45,670
it would be Marquis Wu'an.

250
00:12:46,490 --> 00:12:48,320
But all of this is just our speculation.

251
00:12:48,320 --> 00:12:49,950
