254
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,630
Who knows who will be

255
00:12:55,630 --> 00:12:56,560
his next target.

256
00:13:02,050 --> 00:13:03,250
I want to protect you,

257
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:06,450
but I can't be by your side all the time.

258
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:08,660
Brother Lu, don't worry,

259
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,840
I'll be fine.

260
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,960
But in this life,

261
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:14,130
there are always things
beyond our control.

262
00:13:14,730 --> 00:13:17,260
I'm so afraid that one day
we'll be separated.

263
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:25,950
Brother Lu.

264
00:13:26,370 --> 00:13:28,870
Even if all good things must
come to an end,

265
00:13:29,360 --> 00:13:31,090
as long as we cherish each other

266
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,450
while we're together,

267
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:33,930
and treat each other with sincerity,

268
00:13:33,930 --> 00:13:35,830
we'll have no regrets

269
00:13:36,180 --> 00:13:37,640
and no fear of separation.

270
00:13:39,070 --> 00:13:40,000
It's not enough.

271
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:41,660
Not enough?

272
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:45,440
Then let's hold each other
a little longer.

273
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:51,490
[Shi's Mansion]

274
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:57,810
Brother.

275
00:13:58,570 --> 00:14:01,170
Don't you find this whole affair
rather suspicious?

276
00:14:01,170 --> 00:14:03,540
That's the Prime Minister's mansion
we're talking about.

277
00:14:03,540 --> 00:14:05,980
Even if security isn't as tight
as the palace,

278
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:07,460
there shouldn't have been

279
