is to protect everyone,

289
00:14:32,930 --> 00:14:34,730
and not let more people get hurt.

290
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,490
Brother.

291
00:14:36,900 --> 00:14:38,670
After the Prime Minister's death,

