a peaceful and happy life.

323
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:38,310
Come with me.

324
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,270
I'll be by your side,

325
00:16:40,730 --> 00:16:43,790
protecting you and being with you
every step of the way,

326
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:45,390
as we mourn Grandfather.

327
00:16:48,950 --> 00:16:52,290
If I leave you here alone,

328
00:16:52,930 --> 00:16:54,450
how could I be at ease?

329
00:16:55,430 --> 00:16:58,890
How could Grandfather's spirit
rest in peace?

330
00:17:04,740 --> 00:17:06,000
But I

331
