the Prime Minister's mansion.

333
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,970
When everything settles down,

334
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:17,670
I'll come back with you.

335
00:17:17,849 --> 00:17:18,940
[Dowry List]

336
00:17:21,510 --> 00:17:23,660
Yanyan, trust me.

337
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,290
You'll like my home,

338
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,730
