M-M-Mount Qianya.

342
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:41,570
Is it the infamous Mount Qianya?

343
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:46,250
Yanyan.

344
00:17:47,750 --> 00:17:48,600
You know

345
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:50,920
I'm not a bad person.

346
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:54,980
Mount Qianya isn't like the rumors say.

347
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:58,600
Brother and I have our mission and duties,

