402
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:39,380
You too.

403
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,400
Yanyan, let's go.

404
00:20:48,080 --> 00:20:49,040
I'm leaving now.

405
00:21:02,180 --> 00:21:03,560
