418
00:22:06,110 --> 00:22:07,770
I believe you're good people.

419
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:15,340
These have been my secrets all along.

420
00:22:16,110 --> 00:22:17,780
Today I've told you everything.

421
00:22:17,780 --> 00:22:20,100
Brother Lu, I understand.

