425
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,060
Because...

426
00:22:34,190 --> 00:22:35,250
I want to marry you.

427
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:44,420
Brother Lu.

428
00:22:51,420 --> 00:22:53,480
I had planned to wait until
the country was at peace

429
00:22:53,480 --> 00:22:55,920
