433
00:23:02,470 --> 00:23:03,450
This reminded me

434
00:23:04,650 --> 00:23:06,250
that I can't wait any longer.

435
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:13,390
Ke, I know

436
00:23:13,450 --> 00:23:15,680
you probably didn't expect to
marry so soon.

437
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:18,080
But in this life,
you're the only one for me.

438
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:29,530
Ke, would you be willing?

439
00:23:46,770 --> 00:23:47,540
I am willing.

440
00:23:48,220 --> 00:23:49,030
I am willing.

441
00:23:52,870 --> 00:23:56,490
♪ Fate is holding the thread in my hand ♪

442
00:23:59,040 --> 00:24:02,290
♪ If you appear in dreams once again ♪

443
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:08,550
♪ I am willing to be led by you ♪

444
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:05,950
Thank you, Ke.

445
00:24:06,860 --> 00:24:08,260
Thank you for saying yes.

446
00:24:09,190 --> 00:24:10,690
I've finally waited long enough
for this day.

447
00:24:09,960 --> 00:24:14,240
♪ My heart will never change ♪

448
00:24:10,970 --> 00:24:13,730
Brother Lu, I thank you too.

449
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,570
