00:24:20,680 --> 00:24:22,160
and making a promise with him,

453
00:24:21,680 --> 00:24:27,260
♪ Can't tell if it's bitter or sweet ♪

454
00:24:23,060 --> 00:24:24,980
to meeting you again when I grew up,

