492
00:25:50,270 --> 00:25:50,720
Lu Yi.

493
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:53,920
I'm sure he already has
arrangements in place.

494
00:25:53,920 --> 00:25:56,520
Just keep tracking
his steward's movements.

495
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,400
Yes.

496
00:26:06,590 --> 00:26:07,290
Master.

497
00:26:07,790 --> 00:26:09,220
Recently, all over the streets,

498
00:26:09,220 --> 00:26:11,230
