553
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:46,510
Didn't I tell you to keep an eye
on your sister?

554
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:48,410
Alright, quiet down.

555
00:28:56,400 --> 00:28:57,970
Mr. Lu, please rise.

556
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:02,000
Mr. Lu, you're handsome and well-mannered.

557
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:05,560
You and Ke do seem to share fate.

558
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:08,890
I often hear Ke praising you at home,

559
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:11,280
saying how much you've helped her.

560
00:29:11,590 --> 00:29:12,970
But Ke is still young.

561
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:16,400
You two haven't known each other for long.

562
00:29:17,020 --> 00:29:18,380
As her elder,

563
00:29:19,030 --> 00:29:21,510
I don't know much about
your background and family.

564
00:29:21,510 --> 00:29:23,130
As Ke's mother,

565
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:26,410
how could I be so careless
about my child's marriage?

566
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,800
After all, in the Shi family,

567
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:30,710
she is our only daughter.

568
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:32,750
I understand, Aunt.

569
00:29:33,360 --> 00:29:35,550
Though Ke and I haven't
known each other long,

570
00:29:35,550 --> 00:29:36,350
we have experienced

571
00:29:36,350 --> 00:29:37,810
things others never have.

572
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:40,040
We understand each other deeply.

573
00:29:40,040 --> 00:29:41,570
Please rest assured, Aunt.

574
00:29:41,920 --> 00:29:43,350
After marriage,
I will continue to support Ke,

575
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:45,400
helping her be a good marriage broker,

576
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:47,460
and won't interfere with her career.

577
00:29:50,090 --> 00:29:52,880
I ask for you and Uncle's blessing.

578
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:58,070
Cousin, quick, go to the front hall.

579
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,350
Mr. Lu brought Marriage Broker Zhao

580
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,880
to propose marriage to you.

581
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,330
But your Uncle and Aunt...

582
00:30:02,330 --> 00:30:03,090
So soon?

583
00:30:10,480 --> 00:30:13,880
Chief Matchmaker Tao,
maybe we should ask Ke what she thinks?

584
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:20,590
Hello, Marriage Broker Zhao.

585
00:30:20,590 --> 00:30:22,370
Father, Mother, brothers.

586
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,240
Ke.

587
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,750
Hello to you too, Brother Lu.

588
00:30:24,750 --> 00:30:26,480
You're acting with no decorum.

589
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:29,400
You're a marriage broker yourself.

590
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:32,240
Don't you know the parents must meet first
in these matters?

591
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:35,240
A young lady showing herself like this,
how improper!

592
00:30:37,750 --> 00:30:38,620
Mr. Lu,

593
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:41,010
you know everything about our family.

594
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:44,340
We have two sons and one daughter.

595
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:47,530
May I ask about your family situation?

596
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:50,680
There's only me and my younger brother
Lu Zhuxi at home.

597
00:30:50,680 --> 00:30:52,550
Our parents have both passed away.

598
00:30:52,550 --> 00:30:54,550
We have no known distant relatives.

599
00:30:54,550 --> 00:30:56,660
At Xibao Pavilion, Lu Yi and Li Pan'er

600
00:30:56,790 --> 00:30:59,040
are like family to my brother and me.

601
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:01,710
Then where is your ancestral home?

602
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:08,100
Mother, Brother Lu is from another region.

603
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,930
I wasn't asking you, Shi Fa'ke.

604
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:12,490
One more word and
you'll go back to your room.

605
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:18,980
I'm...

606
00:31:23,750 --> 00:31:25,010
I'm from Mount Qianya.

607
00:31:27,590 --> 00:31:28,610
Mount Qianya?

608
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,770
The one that's crawling with bandits?

609
00:31:32,470 --> 00:31:34,200
Why didn't you tell us earlier?

610
00:31:34,550 --> 00:31:36,830
Mother, Mount Qianya isn't what you think.

611
00:31:36,830 --> 00:31:38,510
Brother Lu and
his younger brother Lu Zhuxi

612
00:31:38,510 --> 00:31:39,440
are good people.

613
00:31:39,590 --> 00:31:41,350
They've never harmed anyone.

614
00:31:41,590 --> 00:31:43,350
Please don't believe those rumors.

615
00:31:43,350 --> 00:31:45,740
Ke, hearsay is unreliable,

616
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,560
but seeing is believing.

617
00:31:47,720 --> 00:31:49,360
If they've done anything wrong,

618
00:31:49,360 --> 00:31:51,290
why would everyone say otherwise?

619
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:53,440
Chief Lu isn't a bad person.

620
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:55,370
Neither is Brother Lu Yi.

621
00:32:00,210 --> 00:32:02,500
Mr. Lu, I cannot accept

622
00:32:03,000 --> 00:32:04,350
this marriage proposal.

623
00:32:04,350 --> 00:32:05,470
Ke is still young,

624
00:32:05,590 --> 00:32:07,120
and she's quite impulsive.

625
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:09,510
You two haven't known each other
long enough.

626
00:32:09,510 --> 00:32:12,040
It's inappropriate to
discuss marriage now.

627
00:32:12,270 --> 00:32:13,480
Ke's two elder brothers

628
00:32:13,480 --> 00:32:15,550
aren't even married yet.

629
00:32:16,110 --> 00:32:17,890
Since ancient times,
it's unheard of for a sister

630
00:32:17,890 --> 00:32:19,510
to marry before her brothers.

631
00:32:19,510 --> 00:32:21,510
Thank you for coming today, Mr. Lu.

632
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,750
Please leave now.

633
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,160
Mother!

634
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:27,160
Brother Lu and I have
known each other for a long time.

635
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:29,870
When he was young,
he wandered into the capital.

636
00:32:29,900 --> 00:32:31,080
That's when we met.

637
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:34,020
I wanted to give him
our family's gold badge,

638
00:32:34,020 --> 00:32:36,350
but he said it was too valuable
and firmly refused.

639
00:32:36,350 --> 00:32:38,020
So I gave him some desserts instead.

640
00:32:38,020 --> 00:32:38,950
We made a promise

641
00:32:39,610 --> 00:32:40,870
that when I came of age,

642
00:32:41,330 --> 00:32:42,730
he would come to marry me.

643
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:45,600
He's here to fulfill
that promise now, Mother.

644
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,600
You won't even listen to
your mother anymore?

645
00:32:47,600 --> 00:32:49,200
I just want to marry Brother Lu!

646
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,300
How shameless!

647
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:53,440
How could a young lady say such things!

648
00:32:57,350 --> 00:32:57,950
Ke.

649
00:33:05,070 --> 00:33:06,740
I understand what you're saying, Aunt.

650
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:09,460
I was indeed rash today,

651
00:33:09,680 --> 00:33:11,240
and I hope you both can forgive me.

652
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:12,330
It's just that Ke is

653
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:15,080
truly the most precious person
in the world to me.

654
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,680
So I will never give up on her.

655
00:33:16,920 --> 00:33:18,200
I will do everything in my power

656
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,120
to protect her,

657
00:33:20,110 --> 00:33:21,110
to make her happy.

658
00:33:21,630 --> 00:33:24,040
I won't let her suffer any grievance
for the rest of her life.

659
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:25,570
She will have my whole heart

660
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:27,510
until the end of our days.

661
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:34,640
So I hope you both will

662
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:35,960
give me some more time

663
00:33:36,470 --> 00:33:37,930
to address your concerns.

664
00:33:50,070 --> 00:33:50,750
Very well.

665
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:52,440
I hope Mr. Lu

666
00:33:52,480 --> 00:33:54,350
can give us an explanation soon.

667
00:33:54,590 --> 00:33:56,660
For now, you may go back.

668
00:33:56,790 --> 00:33:59,390
Mr. Lu, please excuse us
for not seeing you off.

669
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:07,800
Brother Lu.

670
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:08,590
Ke.

671
00:34:19,510 --> 00:34:20,920
Brother Lu, don't...

672
00:34:20,949 --> 00:34:23,210
Don't leave? Or be upset?

673
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:27,100
I meant don't leave so quickly.

674
00:34:27,139 --> 00:34:28,739
I have something to tell you.

675
00:34:28,850 --> 00:34:29,909
Don't be upset.

676
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:32,550
My mother cares deeply about my marriage.

677
00:34:32,550 --> 00:34:34,330
She's afraid I'll act foolishly,

678
00:34:34,330 --> 00:34:36,219
so she's testing us.

679
00:34:36,730 --> 00:34:38,389
Please try to understand her.

680
00:34:43,719 --> 00:34:44,770
Then let me ask you,

681
00:34:44,770 --> 00:34:46,370
what are your true feelings?

682
00:34:50,639 --> 00:34:51,380
I...

683
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:05,120
♪ In this chaotic world, because of you ♪

684
00:35:06,130 --> 00:35:07,450
♪ It's filled with wonder ♪

685
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:10,930
♪ Only you make me unafraid to give ♪

686
00:35:11,720 --> 00:35:12,750
♪ A vow of life and death to live ♪

687
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:15,420
♪ I'll promise you verses ♪

688
00:35:15,320 --> 00:35:16,710
I will definitely marry you.

689
00:35:16,710 --> 00:35:19,120
♪ And all I want you in return ♪

690
00:35:18,870 --> 00:35:19,890
I believe you.

691
00:35:20,650 --> 00:35:26,420
♪ Who cares
who the martial legends may be too? ♪

692
00:35:30,760 --> 00:35:33,010
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

693
00:35:33,490 --> 00:35:35,650
Greetings, Lord Zheng.

694
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:40,940
Fellow marriage brokers,

695
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,330
since Chief Matchmaker Deng passed away,

696
00:35:43,760 --> 00:35:45,760
you have all been working diligently,

697
00:35:45,760 --> 00:35:48,490
handling the matchmaking cases
appropriately.

698
00:35:48,510 --> 00:35:50,640
The court will issue a decree tomorrow

699
00:35:50,700 --> 00:35:53,880
to announce the successor of
the Chief Matchmaker post.

700
00:35:54,590 --> 00:35:57,830
When the time comes, please dress properly

701
00:35:58,070 --> 00:35:59,830
and wear formal attire.

702
00:36:00,320 --> 00:36:01,450
Is that understood?

703
00:36:01,550 --> 00:36:03,930
Yes, My Lord.

704
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:04,840
Good.

705
00:36:13,720 --> 00:36:14,920
Did you hear that, Ke?

706
00:36:15,120 --> 00:36:17,360
It seems the officials know
what they're doing.

707
00:36:17,360 --> 00:36:19,670
The Chief Matchmaker position
will surely be yours.

708
00:36:19,670 --> 00:36:21,970
You'd better take it seriously tomorrow.

709
00:36:21,970 --> 00:36:22,990
You'll be representing

710
00:36:22,990 --> 00:36:25,850
the reputation of the No.1 matchmaker
in the world!

711
00:36:25,850 --> 00:36:27,050
Marriage Broker Zhao, you flatter me.

712
00:36:27,050 --> 00:36:28,510
I'll certainly do my best.

713
00:36:28,790 --> 00:36:31,080
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

714
00:36:37,480 --> 00:36:40,030
[A perfect match]

715
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:44,080
Marriage Broker Shi, I'll be going now.

716
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:51,510
Ke.

717
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:53,450
Brother Lu.

718
00:36:53,550 --> 00:36:55,170
You don't seem happy today.

719
00:36:56,710 --> 00:36:58,610
No, I'm not unhappy.

720
00:36:59,070 --> 00:37:02,580
It's just that they'll announce
the Chief Matchmaker candidate tomorrow.

721
00:37:02,580 --> 00:37:04,170
[A perfect match]

722
00:37:03,550 --> 00:37:05,880
Congratulations, Chief Matchmaker Shi.

723
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:11,250
Brother Lu, we...

724
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:13,540
You...

725
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,720
Ke, do you believe me?

726
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:24,970
That I, Lu Chi,
will marry only you in this lifetime?

727
00:37:25,060 --> 00:37:26,040
If you trust me,

728
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:27,850
once I finish what I need to do,

729
00:37:27,850 --> 00:37:30,380
I'll give your parents
a proper explanation.

730
00:37:30,530 --> 00:37:31,500
Really?

731
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,420
Aren't you upset that
my mother rejected you?

732
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:34,550
Of course it's true.

733
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:37,700
How could I be upset with
my future mother-in-law?

734
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:40,630
[A perfect match]

735
00:37:38,220 --> 00:37:40,080
Tomorrow, you'll officially
take the post.

736
00:37:40,080 --> 00:37:43,210
Come on, I'll take you to
eat something delicious today.

737
00:37:44,110 --> 00:37:47,080
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

738
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:54,180
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

739
00:37:54,670 --> 00:37:55,960
[Official Matchmaking Agency, Fang Yue]

740
00:37:56,150 --> 00:37:57,320
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

741
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:04,140
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

742
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:28,200
Miss, why have you come so early?

743
00:38:28,820 --> 00:38:31,160
The other marriage brokers
haven't arrived yet.

744
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:33,060
If you don't know any marriage brokers,

745
00:38:33,060 --> 00:38:35,390
feel free to tell me about your situation.

746
00:38:35,760 --> 00:38:36,670
Who are you?

747
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:38,210
My name is Shi Fa'ke,

748
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:40,410
I'm a marriage broker from
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

749
00:38:40,410 --> 00:38:42,700
Miss, you are so beautiful.

750
00:38:42,930 --> 00:38:45,730
I wonder what requirements
you have for a partner?

751
00:38:46,090 --> 00:38:49,550
Do you arrange matches for those
who love someone unrequited?

752
00:38:52,040 --> 00:38:55,360
Marriage is about mutual consent and love.

753
00:38:55,560 --> 00:38:57,770
Miss, why are you so persistent?

754
00:38:58,100 --> 00:38:59,580
People are born

755
00:38:59,730 --> 00:39:01,520
with someone meant just for them.

756
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:03,200
If you can't have this person,

757
00:39:03,410 --> 00:39:04,830
then he's not yours.

758
00:39:05,060 --> 00:39:06,990
Let them go when it's time to let go.

759
00:39:07,210 --> 00:39:08,400
Making yourself happy

760
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,930
is also a kind of happiness.

761
00:39:09,990 --> 00:39:11,350
What if you meet someone

762
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:13,860
who's dead set on forcing it through?

763
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:22,670
Miss, may I know your name first?

764
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,320
Fang Yue.

765
00:39:25,190 --> 00:39:27,550
The moon waxes and wanes.

766
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:30,140
A square has all four corners intact.

767
00:39:30,810 --> 00:39:33,170
Miss, your name is quite unique.

768
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:34,590
Is it?

769
00:39:37,150 --> 00:39:38,510
Judging by your accent,

770
00:39:38,670 --> 00:39:40,630
you don't seem to be from the capital.

771
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:42,150
Where are you from,

772
00:39:42,550 --> 00:39:43,500
and do you have any relatives here?

773
00:39:43,500 --> 00:39:44,900
I have no relatives here.

774
00:39:45,150 --> 00:39:47,020
I came to the capital specifically.

775
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:48,680
Specifically to the capital?

776
00:39:49,030 --> 00:39:51,400
Was it to see
that someone you couldn't have?

777
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:53,550
May I ask what kind of man

778
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:55,190
has caught your fancy?

779
00:39:56,870 --> 00:39:59,710
In my eyes, he's brave and extraordinary.

780
00:40:00,210 --> 00:40:03,070
He's skilled in riding,
archery, and horsemanship,

781
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:05,730
a man of letters and arms
who could rule a nation.

782
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:07,890
His status is quite unique.

783
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:10,810
He was widowed early and never remarried.

784
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:11,450
Some say

785
00:40:11,470 --> 00:40:14,670
he must be unwilling to give up
his dalliances with various women.

786
00:40:14,670 --> 00:40:15,800
But that's not true.

787
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:18,970
I know he's destined for greatness,

788
00:40:19,280 --> 00:40:22,810
and is unwilling to be
constrained by romantic entanglements.

789
00:40:23,030 --> 00:40:24,600
Unique status,

790
00:40:25,110 --> 00:40:26,210
widowed...

791
00:40:29,250 --> 00:40:30,860
Who on earth is this man?

792
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:31,970
Ke,

793
00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:35,930
you're here early.

794
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:37,800
And this is?

795
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:39,220
Marriage Broker Zhao, this is Fang...

796
00:40:39,220 --> 00:40:40,480
Marriage Broker Zhao!

797
00:40:40,950 --> 00:40:42,010
Lord Zheng is here.

798
00:40:47,710 --> 00:40:48,760
Miss Fang.

799
00:40:49,080 --> 00:40:51,120
Today, we have important business
at the Agency.

800
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:52,980
Why don't you come back tomorrow?

801
00:40:59,030 --> 00:40:59,490
This...

802
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:05,300
[A Happily Married Couple]

803
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:05,510
Greetings, Lord Zheng.

804
00:41:13,470 --> 00:41:16,270
Fang Yue, Chief Matchmaker of
Suzhou Prefecture.

805
00:41:16,920 --> 00:41:20,320
Intelligent, capable,
and forthright in character.

806
00:41:20,550 --> 00:41:23,030
A true model of a matchmaker.

807
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:26,670
Hence, she is being transferred to
the capital's Official Matchmaking Agency

808
00:41:26,670 --> 00:41:29,110
to take the position of Chief Matchmaker.

809
00:41:30,710 --> 00:41:32,250
How could it be her?

810
00:41:33,150 --> 00:41:34,360
What about Ke?

811
00:41:34,360 --> 00:41:35,000
Yeah.

812
00:41:38,230 --> 00:41:39,460
What's going on?

813
00:41:44,150 --> 00:41:45,150
Listen, Fang Yue,

814
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,570
from now on,

815
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:49,550
you are the Chief Matchmaker of
the capital's Official Matchmaking Agency.

816
00:41:49,550 --> 00:41:51,030
Thank you, Lord Zheng.

817
00:41:51,330 --> 00:41:52,330
Don't mention it.

818
00:41:52,360 --> 00:41:54,820
If there's nothing else,
I'll take my leave.

819
00:41:58,590 --> 00:42:00,020
Take care, Lord Zheng.

820
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:15,280
I haven't had the chance to
introduce myself to everyone yet.

821
00:42:15,280 --> 00:42:16,340
My name is Fang Yue.

822
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:18,870
I'll be working with all of you
from now on.

823
00:42:18,870 --> 00:42:20,520
